Document: Marker3D
Path: godot/classes/class_marker3d.rst
Summary: The gizmo_extents property controls the size of the 3D gizmo cross displayed in the Godot editor for Marker3D nodes.

gizmo_extents (float): Size of the gizmo cross that appears in the editor. Default: 0.25
set_gizmo_extents(value: float): Sets the gizmo cross size
get_gizmo_extents() → float: Returns the current gizmo cross size